criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  > or equal 18 years ;

          -  Candidate for Neuro Zti EVO cochlear implant system, unilateral or bilateral recipient
             ;

          -  Preoperative residual hearing with audiometric thresholds less or equal than 80 dB at
             500 Hz, or higher frequencies

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Medical or psychological conditions which contraindicate surgery (e.g middle ear
             infection, tympanic membrane perforation) ;

          -  Patient with a psychological or linguistic inability to understand the information
             sheet ;

          -  Patient under legal protection or deprived of liberty

          -  Patient included and participating to another trial.
